      <title>沙特或增持顶级建筑商股份以支持经济调整</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-02/saudis-may-raise-stake-in-top-builder-to-support-economic-rejig</link>
      <description><![CDATA[沙特阿拉伯政府可能会增加其在一家陷入困境的建筑集团的股份，该集团被视为该国万亿美元经济转型计划的关键。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-02/saudis-may-raise-stake-in-top-builder-to-support-economic-rejig</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 02 Aug 2024 06:07:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>OPEC+ 减产导致俄罗斯石油钻探量低于纪录水平</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-02/russia-s-oil-drilling-slips-from-record-amid-opec-output-curbs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着俄罗斯进一步加大对 OPEC+ 石油产量的削减，该国石油公司的钻井速度已较去年的记录有所降低。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-02/russia-s-oil-drilling-slips-from-record-amid-opec-output-curbs</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 02 Aug 2024 06:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
