    </item>
    <item>
      <title>市场综述：日本股市跌幅扩大，创 2016 年以来最大跌幅</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着对美国经济和科技公司健康状况的担忧加剧，全球股市抛售加剧。日本股市因预期国内将进一步收紧货币政策而暴跌，进一步加剧了市场情绪。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 22:41:21 GMT</pubDate>
